  <name>SimpleSync</name>
  <summary>Push files to Nextcloud via WebDAV</summary>
  <description>
    <p>SimpleSync is a simple file sync tool for Nextcloud and WebDAV servers. Push local folders to your server with incremental uploads and optional mirror mode.</p>
  </description>

